---
layout: home.njk
meta: 
  title: Loopdash 
  description: Loopdash partners with nonprofits and businesses to deliver expert web design, development, SEO, and hosting solutions that drive results and simplify growth.
pagination:
  data: collections.projects
  size: 10
  alias: projects
sitemap:
  changefreq: weekly
  priority: 1.0
---

<section class="pb-20">
  <div class="home-hero">
    <h1 class="headline">Let's shape <span>tomorrow.</h1>
    <p class="text-6 text-weight-400">Loopdash helps nonprofits turn purpose into progress through design, development, and strategy that drives real impact.</p>
  </div>
  <p class="text-charcoal-light mb-2 text-center mx-auto text-3 container-xxs">Recognized by the publications that move missions forward.</p>
  <div class="slider">
    <div class="slide-track">
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/axios-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white ">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/bloomberg-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white ">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/cnn-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/forbes-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/fortune-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/mashable-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/new-york-times-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/politico-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/the-hill-logo.svg" %}</div>
      <div class="slide svg-white slide-180">{% svgIcon "./src/img/press/the-washington-post-logo.svg" %}</div>
    </div>
  </div> 
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container-sm mx-auto mt-16 text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-11 text-weight-600">Details make the difference.</h2>
    <p class="container-xxs mx-auto">Thoughtful execution, close collaboration, and creative built to make an impact.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="projects container-xl">
    {% for project in projects | sortByDate %}
      {% if project.data.project.featured and project.data.date | isPastDate %}
        <a href="{{project.data.page.url}}" class="reveal project project-{{project.data.project.class}} plausible-event-name=Home+Project+Card+Click+{{project.data.project.class | replace('-', '+')}}">
          <div class="project-details">
            <h4 class="text-4 m-0">{{ project.data.project.name }}</h4>
            <p class="text-3 m-0 text-weight-400">{{ project.data.project.tagline }}</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto mt-4 text-center pb-12">
    <a href="/projects" class="button button-lg button-primary plausible-event-name=More+Projects">More Projects</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container-sm mx-auto mt-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-11 text-weight-600">An extension of your team.</h2>
    <p class="container-xxs mx-auto">When your launch is live, we’re already there — in Slack, in sync, fixing fast and keeping momentum.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="notifications-section">
    <div class='notifications'>
      <div class="notification">
        {% svgIcon "./src/img/team-extension-david.svg", "d" %}
      </div>
      <div class="notification">
        {% svgIcon "./src/img/team-extension-julie.svg", "j" %}
      </div>
      <div class="notification">
        {% svgIcon "./src/img/team-extension-molly.svg", "m" %}
      </div>
      <div class="notification">
        {% svgIcon "./src/img/team-extension-leor.svg", "l" %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center pb-8">
    <a href="/testimonials" class="text-charcoal-light">View testimonials →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="bg-green-waterloo py-10">
<section class="container-sm mx-auto mt-16">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-8 text-weight-600 text-cream-dark">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="text-5 text-weight-400 text-cream-dark">Quick answers to common questions about our services</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="faq-container">
    {% set homepageFaqCount = 0 %}
    {% for question in collections.faq | reverse %}
      {% if "homepage" in question.data.tags and homepageFaqCount < 6 %}
        {% set homepageFaqCount = homepageFaqCount + 1 %}
        {% set question_id = question.data.url | replace("/faq/", "") %}
        <article 
          class="card card-question rounded-7 mb-3 reveal" 
          id="{{ question_id }}" 
          data-id="#{{ question_id }}">
          <div class="card-header" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="content-{{ homepageFaqCount }}">
            <h3 class="text-4 text-cream-dark text-weight-400 my-0">{{ question.data.question }}</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body text-4 text-cream-dark text-weight-400" id="content-{{ homepageFaqCount }}">
            {{ question.templateContent | safe }}
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% if homepageFaqCount == 0 %}
      <div class="text-center py-8">
        <p class="text-4 text-charcoal-light">No FAQs are currently marked for homepage display. Add the "homepage" tag to FAQ files to show them here.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  
  <div class="text-center mt-8">
    <a href="/faq" class="text-white plausible-event-name=Home+FAQ+View+All">View All FAQs</a>
  </div>
</section>
</div>
<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta-container flex-center flex align-items-center">
    <h4 class="text-10 text-weight-600">New clients get $750 in free dev work.</h4>
    <p class="text-5 text-weight-400">We’re giving new clients up to $750 of development work and a complete website audit.</p>
    <a href="/signup" class="shake button button-primary plausible-event-name=Home+CTA+Button+Click">See if you qualify</a>
  </div>
</section>

